description: Silver One Resources Inc., together with its subsidiary, acquires, explores for, and develops silver properties in Canada and the United States. The company holds an option to acquire a 100% interest in the Candelaria silver project located in Nevada. It also holds interest in the Cherokee project covering an area of 5,200 hectares located in Nevada; and an option to acquire a 100% interest in the Phoenix silver property that consists of 86 unpatented lode claims and 2 unpatented placer claims located in Gila County, Arizona. The company was formerly known as BRS Ventures Ltd. and changed its name to Silver One Resources Inc. in September 2016. Silver One Resources Inc. was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Gregory G. Crowe M.Sc., P.Geo., P.Geol.
